{"tid":2156241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：會確保「臨時實驗室」內病毒不會影響附近居民","createTime":"2020-08-14T10:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T13:01:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"954eb2708f86a4f01d2e5d66397e2b031c6ac819","tid":2156241,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始在社交網站發文，指她聯同創科局長薜永恒，昨日到訪中山紀念公園體育館，參觀臨時實驗室的搭建情況，指16個實驗室大致準備就緒。她又指，全部實驗室都符合第二級生物安全水平，亦會採取妥善的感染控制措施，確保衛生，不會影響附近居民或環境。 <br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又重申，「普及社區檢測計劃」屬自願性質，收集或使用任何個人資料，都會嚴守私隱條例，加密儲存在政府數據中心伺服器內，不會傳送至境外；檢測樣本亦不會送出香港以外，檢測完會銷毁。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2352408&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=f878caa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352408</a>"},{"pid":"f10cb01955e43cc5b617a4a04e5e32f1f9ca1990","tid":2156241,"uid":359626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"57b604af4f2c66c9c4f5dadd070a3e487126a149","tid":2156241,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"Hi 樓主"},{"pid":"6e6409086273a2e8f92fd3c52557ab75e051dce3","tid":2156241,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3084a83a85313bee5df5f10729523f66d5cd0e22","tid":2156241,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b604af4f2c66c9c4f5dadd070a3e487126a149","tid":2156241,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"Hi 樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc72991f30117f4fc5e00c47efe4096ab1bcbc","tid":2156241,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f10cb01955e43cc5b617a